  "title": "Supply Chain Professional",
  "description": "<p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Professional graduated in Engineering with experience in multidisciplinary engineering projects in the oil and gas sector, and in designing oil exploration platform</li><li>The professional shall be able to execute the following activities, at least:</li><li>Monitor and expedite the issuance of pending engineering and vendor documents</li><li>Analyze project documentation</li><li>Follow up and expedite change control in the project for the issuance of as-built documents</li><li>Prepare PowerPoint presentations and dashboards in Excel</li><li>Expedite supply issues and late deliveries with equipment suppliers</li><li>Mon - Thu: 0730 - 1730hrs</li><li>Fri: 0730 - 1630hrs = total 44hrs/week</li><li>location - TBY yard.</li></ul>",
